---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Find a Telehealth Psychologist for Anxiety in Sydney | Connect"
  description="Tell us what you are looking for and we will connect you with an AHPRA-registered telehealth psychologist specialising in anxiety in Sydney. Response within 1 business day."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 620px;">

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Find a Psychologist
      </p>

      <h1>Find a Telehealth Psychologist for Anxiety</h1>
      <p>Tell us a little about what you are looking for and we will connect you with a suitable telehealth psychologist in Sydney within 1 business day. There is no obligation; submitting this form does not commit you to anything.</p>

      <div class="info-box" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p><strong>What happens next:</strong> When you submit this form, your details are sent to our network of AHPRA-registered psychologists in Sydney who specialise in anxiety and offer telehealth. A psychologist will be in touch within 1 business day to introduce themselves and discuss availability. You can decide whether to proceed from there.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Form: posts to Google Apps Script, which appends to the submissions Sheet -->
      <form
        method="POST"
        action="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbxlGPGS_ZjNlbF0uBl_WC0yp3-J6TSl_DYiYqUIjxcitQyCDKDO60E0gOSxFfxwZmQz/exec"
        style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 2rem;"
      >
        <!-- Which site this came from -->
        <input type="hidden" name="_site" value="anxiety-sydney" />
        <!-- Redirect to thank-you page after successful submission (absolute URL for the script redirect) -->
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/connect/thank-you/" />
        <!-- Honeypot spam field: the handler ignores submissions where this is filled -->
        <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display: none;" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <label for="name" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Your name *</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name"
            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
          />
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <label for="email" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Email address *</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email"
            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
          />
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <label for="suburb" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">Sydney suburb or area (optional)</label>
          <input type="text" id="suburb" name="suburb" placeholder="e.g. Inner West, Northern Beaches, Parramatta" autocomplete="address-level2"
            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; background: var(--color-bg);"
          />
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
          <label for="notes" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--color-text);">What are you hoping to get help with? (optional)</label>
          <p style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">For example: the type of anxiety you experience, any preferences for days or times, or anything else that is useful to know. You are not required to share anything you are not comfortable disclosing.</p>
          <textarea id="notes" name="notes" rows="4"
            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit; resize: vertical; background: var(--color-bg);"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="btn btn--primary plausible-event-name=Form+Submit"
          style="width: 100%; font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.9rem;"
        >
          Connect me with a psychologist
        </button>

        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 1rem; text-align: center;">
          Your information will only be used to connect you with a suitable psychologist. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </form>

      <hr />

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2rem;">Useful before you book</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/">What does a telehealth psychologist cost?</a> Fees, Medicare rebates, and how to get a Mental Health Treatment Plan.</li>
        <li><a href="/guides/does-online-therapy-work-for-anxiety/">Does online therapy actually work for anxiety?</a> What the evidence shows.</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
